			dependencies: ["7A05000000000104"]
			description: [
				"&8[ FIELD REPORT — THE ONE BELOW ]&r"
				""
				"&7Every deep expedition that recorded it agrees on one thing: you hear it long before you see it, and it comes from further down than the surveys go. What it leaves behind is a recording of a sound that has no source.&r"
				""
				"&8Objective: recover a Deep Echo.&r"
			]
