			dependencies: ["7A05000000000106"]
			description: [
				"&8[ FIELD REPORT — THE MAN ]&r"
				""
				"&7It stands at the edge of the fog and watches. It does not approach while you look. The residue it leaves has no composition our instruments recognise, and it does not disperse.&r"
				""
				"&8Objective: recover Fog Residue.&r"
